# Source specification PDFs are the publishers' to distribute, not ours to vendor — for
# ANY state, at any depth (corpus/SS2026.pdf, corpus/nd/2025.pdf, ...). This is also the
# repo-level half of the reuse gate: an uncleared state's source can never be committed.
